@startuml Azure_AzureStack-QuickStart-Templates

!define RECTANGLE class

skinparam component {
  BackgroundColor<<Security>> LightYellow
  BackgroundColor<<Performance>> LightGreen
  BackgroundColor<<Connectivity>> LightBlue
}

[Azure Resource Manager] as ARM
[Azure Stack] as AzureStack
[Public Azure] as Azure
[KeyVault] <<Security>>
[Load Balancer] <<Performance>>
[VPN Gateway] <<Connectivity>>

package "Deployment Templates" {
  [ARM Templates]
  [PowerShell Scripts]
  [Shell Scripts]
}

package "Infrastructure Components" {
  [Virtual Machines]
  [Virtual Networks]
  [Storage Accounts]
  [Network Security Groups]
}

package "Application Platforms" {
  [Docker Swarm]
  [Service Fabric]
  [Hadoop]
  [Ethereum Blockchain]
}

package "High Availability Solutions" {
  [SQL Server Farms]
  [Remote Desktop Services]
}

package "Validation & Testing" {
  [VM Bootstorm]
  [IOStorm]
}

ARM --> Deployment Templates : uses
Deployment Templates --> AzureStack : deploys to
Deployment Templates --> Azure : deploys to
Deployment Templates --> Infrastructure Components : creates
Deployment Templates --> Application Platforms : sets up
Deployment Templates --> "High Availability Solutions" : configures
Deployment Templates --> "Validation & Testing" : runs

KeyVault ..> Deployment Templates : provides secrets
Load Balancer ..> Infrastructure Components : distributes traffic
VPN Gateway ..> Infrastructure Components : connects networks

@enduml